{"tid":2005001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呀媽因為我而藍變黃","createTime":"2020-05-06T23:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T23:57:58.000Z","uid":126621,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"17227d99550d1707abc028ae0403400e5691a156","tid":2005001,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T23:23:32.000Z","msg":"涉及本人, 唔信嘅可以走先, 但絕對真人真事<br />\n<br />\n我呀媽信我但藍絲,成日在屋企向我祈禱, 原本呀媽信哂tvb, 開口埋口就黑衣人暴徒, 後尾佢屎忽痕走去向我問：<br />\n媽: 班黑衣人搞搞陣破壞香港, 係咪會有報應?<br />\n(我: 唔係)<br />\n媽: 佢地搞破壞係咪令香港變差?<br />\n(我: 唔係)<br />\n媽: 佢地係咪為香港著想?<br />\n(我: 係)<br />\n媽: 佢地咁做係咪會令香港變好?<br />\n(我: 係)<br />\n<br />\n以上重覆問咗成晚, 答案全部一樣, 呀媽睇到呆撚咗, 但又唔鋸, 第二朝再問:<br />\n媽: 警察係咪真係黑衣人講嘅做咗咁多壞事?<br />\n(我: 係)<br />\n媽: 尚德個𡃁仔(周同學)係咪真係比警察推落去死?<br />\n(我: 係)<br />\n媽: 香港因為班黑衣人變差?<br />\n(我: 唔係)<br />\n我搭嗲: 因為班畜牲支那班賤狗呀<br />\n媽: 係咪因為大陸人而變到咁差?<br />\n(我 笑)<br />\n媽: 班警察係咪會有報應?<br />\n(我: 笑)<br />\n<br />\n上面又重覆問咗成朝, 答案又一樣, 呀媽又呆撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時成日阻止我屌鳩支那畜, 自此之後逢親我屌都唔出聲. 平時我有夜跑嘅習慣, 之後都叫我唔好夜晚落街, 好危險"},{"pid":"cb16899bd2e6e6b3096f0d30ab776dd54c16a87a","tid":2005001,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T23:25:03.000Z","msg":"(我: 笑)"},{"pid":"483653bb0c7c3e44fb819525b20f5ba90185fcef","tid":2005001,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb16899bd2e6e6b3096f0d30ab776dd54c16a87a","tid":2005001,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T23:25:03.000Z","msg":"(我: 笑)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T23:25:42.000Z","msg":"笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c658a20bd04e10eccd3b71225eb2455155316e7","tid":2005001,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T23:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYSpOjy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYSpOjy.png&h=74f86f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[遍地開花]輪到我哋白卡人士發聲啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1375646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1375646</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"ad7df76507b844c8b4cab0204413a193a396d5e8","tid":2005001,"uid":355697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T23:29:12.000Z","msg":"乜咁就叫黃？"},{"pid":"9913fb39431a23feee2d7dc32a3bcfcaf3556c0e","tid":2005001,"uid":326712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad7df76507b844c8b4cab0204413a193a396d5e8","tid":2005001,"uid":355697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T23:29:12.000Z","msg":"乜咁就叫黃？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T23:40:43.000Z","msg":"D牙黃"},{"pid":"e8cf1a5267bae5fc8fc35e524fd82f4f163fe563","tid":2005001,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T23:57:58.000Z","msg":"炒post狗"}]}